casebody.data:
Owen D. LEAVITT
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 191P16. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 19, 2016. Owen D. Leavitt, for Leavitt, Owen D. Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Michael D. Waters, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 18th of May 2016 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Warren County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 19th of May 2016."
